org.jbei.ice.lib.parsers.genbank

Class GenBankParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.lib.parsers.AbstractParser
      • org.jbei.ice.lib.parsers.genbank.GenBankParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDNAParser

    public class GenBankParser
extends AbstractParser
    Genbank parser and generator. The Genbank file format is defined in gbrel.txt located at ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genbank/gbrel.txt

    This parser also handles some incorrectly formatted and obsolete genbank files.

    Author:
    Timothy Ham
